        <ul class="text-base-content/70 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong class="text-secondary">Morning Visualization:</strong> Spend 5 minutes imagining successful interactions for the day</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-secondary">Posture Checks:</strong> Set phone reminders to check and correct your posture hourly</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-secondary">Eye Contact Practice:</strong> In conversations, hold eye contact for 3-5 seconds before looking away</li>
